@startuml
title tile_sim の構成

top to bottom direction
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing true
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam defaultFontName Yu Gothic UI
skinparam defaultFontSize 18
skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 24
  BorderColor black
  BackgroundColor #f7fbff
  FontColor black
}
skinparam ArrowColor black
skinparam ranksep 20
skinparam nodesep 20

rectangle "main.js" as MainJs
rectangle "controller.js" as ControllerJs
rectangle "camera.js" as CameraJs
rectangle "mission.js" as MissionJs
rectangle "terrain.js /\nconstants.js" as TerrainJs
rectangle "alpha_actor.js" as AlphaActorJs
rectangle "enemy_units.js /\nsupport_units.js" as EnemyUnitsJs
rectangle "human.glb runtime" as HumanRuntime

MainJs --> ControllerJs
MainJs --> CameraJs
MainJs --> MissionJs
MainJs --> TerrainJs
ControllerJs --> AlphaActorJs
MissionJs --> EnemyUnitsJs
AlphaActorJs --> HumanRuntime

ControllerJs -[hidden]right-> CameraJs
CameraJs -[hidden]right-> MissionJs
AlphaActorJs -[hidden]right-> EnemyUnitsJs

note top of MainJs
役割を分けて読むと tile_sim の設計が追いやすい
end note
@enduml
